OL,5, Glasgow's Kelvingrove Museum and Art   
OL,6, Galleries and City Chambers are set to 
OL,7, be sold by the city council to settle  
OL,8, equal pay claims.                      
OL,10,FCouncillors approved a strategy to sell
OL,11,Fthese and other buildings, valued at   
OL,12,Fabout #200 million, to a council-owned 
OL,13,Fproperty firm and lease them back.     
OL,15,FThe council still owes millions from a 
OL,16,Flong-running equal pay dispute, mainly 
OL,17,Finvolving female workers.              
OL,19,FIt brought more than 12,000 equal pay  
OL,20,Fclaims over a decade.                  
